description.en: A license for the unlimited use of a pattern in SKIN sequencing, once activated and inside your SKINR collection. The digital sequence of this pattern license has not been bound, allowing for its unlimited use. However, every time you sequence a design using this pattern you must provide Alignment Sequencer to bind the unique SKIN licenses you are producing.

name.ja: エグゼクティブ・ターン - 無制限
